  "body": "Currently sync starts when:\n- there is at least 5 peers OR,\n- after 10 seconds.\n\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/eth/sync.go#L32-L33\n\nAllow a user to control these values.\n\nMoreover, there is no point to wait for 5 peers if the user set peer max number to 3.\n",
